Yusuf (Persian na Arabic: يوسف Yūsuf) bụ aha nwoke sitere na Arabic nke pụtara "Chineke na-abawanye" (na nsọpụrụ, ike na mmetụta).Onye isi mara mma, Onye ndu
Ndị Peshia, Kurd na ndị Turkey jikwa aha ahụ
Ọ bụ Arabic aha ya na aha Hibru Josef na aha Bekee bụ Joseph
Ndị Alakụba, ndị Arab, Kurd, ndị Turkey, na ndị Peshia nke okpukpe ndị ọzọ na-eji aha ahụ
Ọ na-ejekwa ozi dị ka aha nna unisex (maka nwoke na nwanyị).
